ine translation, abstractive summarization, and task-oriented dialogue, where hierarchical context integration is critical. Furthermore, the routing weights provide intrinsic interpretability, allowing analysis of how the model shifts focus across encoder depths during generation—a capability absent in standard Transformers.",
